aces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSky dive用左 500 - 600 <br />\n係Interlaken到跳 個景好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣打得唔係幾清楚唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n但係你如果5萬 兩個人 十日我覺得實夠（唔計機票）"},{"pid":"677b6355294b21d32830133e5d4b1ce8c1ea337d","tid":185071,"uid":43529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d 野食好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去過一次 但瑞士真係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家睇咗間民宿都係100usd到 <br />\n果到有得煮應該會平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得煮一定要煮 <br />\n抵好多<br />\n果陣無得我煮<br />\n我又唔想點洗錢食野 成日餓住個肚食sandwich 但都唔係平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d099f957c7da8ec40263230343ee24ce5e9e0b","tid":185071,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"我講緊當地洗費 5萬到 純粹覺得瑞士好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1c27e7349b2443a5734c627994cb54e7177c4b","tid":185071,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"瑞士啲物價真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d18068165affa76063d62674d6704656e1b99f","tid":185071,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:15:19.000Z","msg":"跪求瑞士餐廳推介<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/150277/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/150277/page/2?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid